    <detaileddescription>
<para><bold>IADLXDisplaySettingsChangedEvent3</bold> is an extension interface to <ref refid="_d_o_x__i_a_d_l_x_display_settings_changed_event" kindref="compound">IADLXDisplaySettingsChangedEvent</ref>, and provides methods to check for changes to the Dynamic Refresh Rate Control and FreeSync color accuracy settings.</para>
<para><table rows="4" cols="2"><row>
<entry thead="no"><para>InterfaceId:</para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>IADLXDisplaySettingsChangedEvent3</para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para>Smart Pointer Interface Name:</para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>IADLXDisplaySettingsChangedEvent3Ptr</para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para>Inherits:</para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para><ref refid="_d_o_x__i_a_d_l_x_display_settings_changed_event2" kindref="compound">IADLXDisplaySettingsChangedEvent2</ref></para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para>Inherited By:</para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>N/A</para>
</entry></row>
</table>
</para>
<para>The <bold>IADLXDisplaySettingsChangedEvent3</bold> interface is obtained from the <ref refid="_d_o_x__i_a_d_l_x_display_settings_changed_event" kindref="compound">IADLXDisplaySettingsChangedEvent</ref> interface or from any of its extension interfaces using <ref refid="_d_o_x__i_a_d_l_x_interface__query_interface" kindref="compound">QueryInterface</ref>.</para>
